  • Deprecated Interfaces 
    Interface and Description
    oracle.kv.table.ExecutionFuture
    since 3.3 in favor of ExecutionFuture
    oracle.kv.table.StatementResult
    since 3.3 in favor of StatementResult
    oracle.kv.stats.StoreIteratorMetrics
    since 3.4, no longer supported.
  • Deprecated Methods 
    Method and Description
    oracle.kv.table.TableAPI.execute(String)
    since 3.3 in favor of KVStore.execute(java.util.List<oracle.kv.Operation>)
    oracle.kv.table.TableAPI.executeSync(String)
    since 3.3 in favor of KVStore.executeSync(java.lang.String)
    oracle.kv.stats.NodeMetrics.getDataCenterName()
    replaced by NodeMetrics.getZoneName()
    oracle.kv.StoreIteratorConfig.getMaxResultsBatches()
    since 3.4, no longer supported. Returns the value set by setMaxResultsBatches().
    oracle.kv.table.TableIteratorOptions.getMaxResultsBatches()
    since 3.4, no longer supported. Returns the value set by deprecated TableIteratorOptions constructor.
    oracle.kv.KVStoreConfig.getOpenTimeout(TimeUnit)
    replaced by KVStoreConfig.getSocketOpenTimeout(java.util.concurrent.TimeUnit)
    oracle.kv.stats.KVStats.getStoreIteratorMetrics()
    since 3.4, no longer supported. All of the methods of the returned StoreIteratorMetrics object will return 0.
    oracle.kv.lob.PartialLOBException.isPartiallyDeleted()
    Use the getPartialStateMethod() instead
    oracle.kv.StoreIteratorConfig.setMaxResultsBatches(int)
    since 3.4, no longer supported.
    oracle.kv.KVStoreConfig.setOpenTimeout(long, TimeUnit)
    replaced by KVStoreConfig.setSocketOpenTimeout(long, java.util.concurrent.TimeUnit)
  • Deprecated Constructors 
    Constructor and Description
    oracle.kv.table.TableIteratorOptions(Direction, Consistency, long, TimeUnit, int, int, int)
    since 3.4, no longer supported. replaced by TableIteratorOptions.TableIteratorOptions(Direction, Consistency, long, TimeUnit, int, int)
